{"article_id":"mKWWQp9ojQA3iXJj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Two Amtrak personnel were killed","depth":11},{"id":1,"text":"and over 100 others were injured","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"when an Amtrak passenger train collided with a parked CSX freight train early Sunday just outside the capital of South Carolina ,","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"officials said .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"The South Carolina Emergency Management Division said","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Amtrak 91 was traveling from New York to Miami","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"when it collided with the CSX train in Pine Ridge around 2:35 a.m .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"\" It appears to me","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"that the CSX train was on the track","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"it was supposed to be on , \"","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"South Carolina Gov . Henry McMaster said at a news conference .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"\" It appears Amtrak was on the wrong track .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"That ' s what it appears to me . \"","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Amtrak said in a statement","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"the train 's lead engine derailed ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"as did some passenger cars","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"that was carrying eight crew members and approximately 139 passengers on board .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"TV footage from the crash scene showed the aftermath of the collision ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"with the Amtrak engine on its side and its front crumpled .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"McMaster said","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"the two people","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"killed in the crash","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"were Amtrak personnel","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"and 116 people were taken to area hospitals .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Lexington County Coroner Margaret Fisher identified the two victims of Amtrak crash as engineer Michael Kempf , 54 , and conductor Michael Cella , 36 .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Fisher said","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"that several people remain in critical condition .","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"`` We have anywhere from scratches and bumps to more severe broken bones , ''","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"Lexington County spokesman Harrison Cahill told reporters .","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"`` It appears to me","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"that the CSX train was on the track","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"it was supposed to be on .","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"It appears Amtrak was on the wrong track .","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"That ' s what it appears to me. \"","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"- South Carolina Gov . Henry McMaster","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"McMaster said","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"the first engine of the freight train was `` torn up , ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"while the engine on the Amtrak train is `` barely recognizable . ''","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"The governor added","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that no one was on the CSX train at the time of the crash ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"and the Amtrak train was estimated to be going 59 mph .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"`` Two trains ,","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"that 's as forceful","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"as can get , ''","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"adding","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"that `` I would ask","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"this is a Sunday ,","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"everyone go to church","depth":15},{"id":49,"text":"and say a prayer for these people involved . ''","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"In its statement , Amtrak","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"it is cooperating fully with the National Transportation Safety Board ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"which is leading the investigation .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"`` CSX owns and controls the Columbia Subdivision","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"where the accident occurred , ''","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Amtrak said .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"`` CSX maintains all of the tracks and signal systems .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"CSX controls the dispatching of all trains ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"including directing the signal systems","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"which control the access to sidings and yards . ''","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Hospital officials told Fox News","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"they have received nearly 90 patients from the crash ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"but most of which have been discharged already .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Lexington Medical Center spokeswoman Jennifer Wilson said","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"the facility received 27 patients from the crash ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"all of which had `` minor injuries ''","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"and since been discharged .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"A spokesperson from Palmetto Health said","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"they received 62 patients","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"as a result of the crash at three of their facilities .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"The health care network said","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"there are two patients","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"that are expected to be admitted ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"but most are expected to be released","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"after they are evaluated and treated .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"`` The thoughts of all our team members are with the family and friends of those injured in this accident , ''","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Palmetto Health spokesperson Tammie Epps said .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"`` Palmetto Health is coordinating with local authorities , Amtrak and the American Red Cross","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"to assist these families in any way possible . ''","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"No immediate information was available about the CSX train ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"but SCMED Public Information Officer Derrec Becker told reporters","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"that officials are working","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"to secure a fuel leak","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"that resulted from the spill .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"As of now , 5,000 gallons of diesel fuel has spilled","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"and crews are trying to secure the leak ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"according to Becker .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"`` There is no danger to anyone in the nearby area of Lexington County , ''","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Becker told `` FOX & friends Weekend . ''","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Amtrak officials gathered up luggage and other belongings","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"and within hours put passengers aboard buses to their destinations .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Before being sent on their way ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"those","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"who were not hurt","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"were taken to a shelter ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"and local businesses provided coffee and breakfast .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"Amtrak said","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that anyone with questions","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"regarding passengers on the train","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"can contact them at 1-800-523-9101 .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"South Carolina 's Red Cross chapter tweeted","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"that emergency responders were at the scene .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"The people","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"who were n't hurt","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"were taken in patrol cars to a shelter ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Lexington County Sheriff 's spokesman Adam Myrick said .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"`` We know","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"they are shaken up quite a bit .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"We know","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"this is like nothing else","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"they have ever been through .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"So we wanted to get them out of the cold ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"get them out of the weather -","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"get them to a warm place , ''","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"Myrick said .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"The National Transportation Safety Board said","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"it was launching a `` Go Team ''","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"to investigate the deadly crash","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"and plans a press conference for later in the day .","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"President Trump tweeted about the crash on Sunday ,","depth":4},{"id":120,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"`` my thoughts and prayers are with all of the victims","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"involved in this mornings train collision in South Carolina .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"Thank you to our incredible First Responders for the work","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"they ' ve done ! ''","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"Trump was briefed on the train accident","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"and is receiving regular updates ,","depth":5},{"id":127,"text":"according to Deputy White House Press Secretary Lindsay Walters .","depth":4},{"id":128,"text":"This is the third Amtrak crash since December .","depth":2},{"id":129,"text":"On Dec. 18 , an Amtrak train derailed in Washington state ,","depth":4},{"id":130,"text":"killing three people","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"and injuring dozens more .","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"Just last week , one person in a truck died","depth":5},{"id":133,"text":"when an Amtrak crash","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"carrying Republican members of Congress","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"struck the vehicle at a crossing .","depth":6},{"id":136,"text":"Two other people in the vehicle were severely injured .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":273,"left":264,"right":272,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":255,"right":263,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":251,"right":254,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":189,"right":250,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":1